OL,3,CFormer footballer Kevin Campbell 'died
OL,4,Cof natural causes'
OL,6,FFormer Premier League footballer Kevin
OL,7,FCampbell died of natural causes -
OL,8,Fdespite delays in diagnosing a rare
OL,9,Fheart infection, an inquest has found.
OL,11,FThe striker, who was best known for
OL,12,Fhis time at Arsenal and Everton, died
OL,13,Fat the age of 54 at Manchester Royal
OL,14,FInfirmary (MRI) in 2024.
OL,16,FManchester Coroners' Court heard on
OL,17,FMonday, 14 April, that he was said to
OL,18,Fbe fit and well until around January
OL,19,F2024, when he was first admitted to
OL,20,FMRI for seven weeks.
