OL,3,CFormer footballer Kevin Campbell 'died
OL,4,Cof natural causes'
OL,6,FTests showed he was suffering from
OL,7,Fsevere heart and kidney failure but
OL,8,Ffollowing treatment, including
OL,9,Fdialysis, he was deemed healthy enough
OL,10,Fto be discharged.
OL,12,FCampbell lost weight during his
OL,13,Fhospital stay from 124kg to 98kg, but
OL,14,Fit had plummeted to just 59kg when he
OL,15,Fwas readmitted two months later on 17
OL,16,FMay.
