OL,3,CFormer footballer Kevin Campbell 'died
OL,4,Cof natural causes'
OL,6,FArea Coroner for Manchester, Zak
OL,7,FGolombek, said Campbell was "very
OL,8,Funwell" at that stage and medics felt
OL,9,Fthere was some continuation of the
OL,10,Fheart and kidney failure, with signs
OL,11,Fof an infection of unknown cause.
OL,13,FHis condition continued to deteriorate
OL,14,Fas further investigations and tests in
OL,15,Fearly June confirmed a diagnosis of
OL,16,Finfective endocarditis. Medical
OL,17,Ftreatment then continued until his
OL,18,Fdeath from multi-organ failure.
